{
  "page": "Blood (horse)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Blood</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Thrumugnyr_on_the_hunt.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Thrumugnyr on the hunt.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/70/Thrumugnyr_on_the_hunt.jpg/350px-Thrumugnyr_on_the_hunt.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/70/Thrumugnyr_on_the_hunt.jpg/525px-Thrumugnyr_on_the_hunt.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/70/Thrumugnyr_on_the_hunt.jpg/700px-Thrumugnyr_on_the_hunt.jpg 2x\" /></a><div><a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Bolton\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ramsay Bolton\">Ramsay Bolton</a> astride Blood, hunting with his <a href=\"/index.php/Hunting_Hounds_of_Ramsay_Bolton\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hunting Hounds of Ramsay Bolton\">pack of feral dogs</a> © Thrumugnyr</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Owner</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Species</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">Horse</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_3\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 3\">Season 3</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_4\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 4\">4</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_5\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 5\">5</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_6\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 6\">6</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Blood</b> is <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Bolton\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ramsay Bolton\">Ramsay Bolton</a>'s steed.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_(horse)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Blood_(horse)\" title=\"Category:Images of Blood (horse)\">Images of Blood (horse)</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Blood is a red stallion with a temper to match his master’s.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_(horse)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_(horse)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ramsay has \"<a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Reek</a>\" see to Blood when he returns to <a href=\"/index.php/Barrowton\" title=\"Barrowton\">Barrowton</a> after searching for the missing <a href=\"/index.php/Jared_Frey\" title=\"Jared Frey\">Jared</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Frey\" title=\"Rhaegar Frey\">Rhaegar</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Symond_Frey\" title=\"Symond Frey\">Symond Frey</a>. As Reek leads him to the stables, he has to hop aside when the stallion tries to kick him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_(horse)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 32\">Chapter 32</a>, Reek III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183855\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.062 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.229 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 442/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9938/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5126/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 942/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 805/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.62 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  218.709      1 -total\n 96.55%  211.172      1 Template:Infobox_animal_character\n 95.95%  209.850      1 Template:Infobox\n  5.64%   12.329      5 Template:Infobox_value\n  2.83%    6.189      2 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.64%    5.766      2 Template:Ref\n  1.67%    3.660      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.69%    1.509      1 Template:References\n  0.40%    0.871      1 Template:Main_other\n  0.21%    0.453      1 Template:Nowrap\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:8433-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403183855 and revision id 297923\n -->\n",
